-- UniCredit Hires Carlo Maria Galli to Head Southern Europe Derivative Sales
-- B y   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i   a n d   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i
-- 2010-10-04T11:07:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-04/unicredit-hires-galli-to-head-southern-europe-derivative-sales.html
UniCredit SpA hired Carlo Maria Galli
to head its institutional equity derivative sales in Southern
Europe, according to an e-mailed statement today.  Previously Galli was head of product innovation and
development at Eurizon Capital Sgr, it said. UniCredit also said
it appointed Alberto Llaneza as equity derivative sales in
Spain.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chiara Remondini at 
 cremondini@bloomberg.net  